   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Favorinos to Kalantion, greetings. Demand back for me from N. N. bailiff, 1.400 dr(achmas) and from Peteuris 2.400 dr(achmas), in total 3.800 dr(achmas). I pray for your health, my dearest."</ab>
         </div>
